    "description": "加入官方Q群：961849645，共商重塑火星大计！<br><br>火星，地球近邻，但寒冷又贫瘠。<br><br>你，人类，基地指挥官，胆大而心细。<br><br>来到火星，为人类打造一颗宜居星球，合情又合理。<br><br>你打算怎么做？<br><br>要不……大致看一看下面的说明书？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1395760/extras/e22b2ba21c30f80995c3c4952ef39674.avif?t=1760234871\" width=623 height=177 /></span><br><br>开局一颗火星，着陆地点你随便选，当然建议选高一点的地方，那里风电强劲，还不会被以后的火星海洋淹没。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1395760/extras/920f6df2b1080dbdf7a41d62e3105d9a.poster.avif?t=1760234871\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1395760/extras/920f6df2b1080dbdf7a41d62e3105d9a.webm?t=1760234871\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1395760/extras/920f6df2b1080dbdf7a41d62e3105d9a.mp4?t=1760234871\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>游戏中使用的全真火星地形数据库。地理命名，高度场都与真实火星一致。你可以到处看看，为将来到火星上开垦种地选个风水宝地。<br><br>如果谨慎一些，你可以在好好观察在本局游戏中，火星上的各项矿物资源分布。来火星已经够不容易了，还是选块矿产富庶的地方造起来。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1395760/extras/e8342bfd9be675de9d254bd3abd09a7b.avif?t=1760234871\" width=623 height=177 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1395760/extras/bec0215f103538ee1ee1b02cef4c0d71.poster.avif?t=1760234871\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1395760/extras/bec0215f103538ee1ee1b02cef4c0d71.webm?t=1760234871\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1395760/extras/bec0215f103538ee1ee1b02cef4c0d71.mp4?t=1760234871\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>采矿！造材料！拉电网！接水管！盖房子！摇人！造工厂！搞科研！<br><br>你开始忙起来，工程车也忙起来，火星上的居民也都给我忙碌起来！<br><br>看着欣欣向荣的火星基地，你也许会抑制不住嘴角上扬，一个优秀的基地建设者，带领大家正在创造美好生活，你做到了！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1395760/extras/cd50b4ff1f0bfa47b29997d990850f4d.avif?t=1760234871\" width=623 height=177 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1395760/extras/37a3fa0c13dcf6724613eb7ffafb8ef1.poster.avif?t=1760234871\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1395760/extras/37a3fa0c13dcf6724613eb7ffafb8ef1.webm?t=1760234871\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1395760/extras/37a3fa0c13dcf6724613eb7ffafb8ef1.mp4?t=1760234871\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>你可以直接操控工程车，但你不能直接操控任何火星居民，因为他们是人，有自由意志的人。<br><br>但是，你依然有很多方法可以调控大家的行为：工资，房租，市场价格，政策宣传……<br><br>别做得太狠，麻烦给这些亿万里迢迢前来火星的打工人一个体面的生活。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1395760/extras/c020f13ea1534ce985a9e69b5b3fe295.avif?t=1760234871\" width=623 height=177 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1395760/extras/78ae8cad75ddd91ac574f57611d55aaf.poster.avif?t=1760234871\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1395760/extras/78ae8cad75ddd91ac574f57611d55aaf.webm?t=1760234871\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1395760/extras/78ae8cad75ddd91ac574f57611d55aaf.mp4?t=1760234871\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>物质是守恒的，你挖了矿，就会留下矿坑。<br><br>同理，如果有座山挡住了你的基地规划，那就把它挖了做矿。<br><br>如果有片海拦了你前进的道路，那就把它填了变坦途。<br><br>如果你挖的够深，或者填得够高；在太空中也能看到你的杰作。这……也许就是……奇观？<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1395760/extras/f437b7811d95c75b979613797cee7ccc.avif?t=1760234871\" width=623 height=177 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1395760/extras/db42041cf3a572293e100a6c44ab51b2.poster.avif?t=1760234871\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1395760/extras/db42041cf3a572293e100a6c44ab51b2.webm?t=1760234871\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1395760/extras/db42041cf3a572293e100a6c44ab51b2.mp4?t=1760234871\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>噢对了，别忘记我们是来干啥的，重塑火星，打造一颗人类宜居星球！<br><br>这可不是一件容易的事儿，你得一步步攀科技，搞生产，解决好基地自循环问题后，就能向火星开始全力输出。<br><br>填充大气，改造磁场，提升温度，重建海洋，植树造林……<br><br>你也许会对庞大的数值和工作量感到绝望。但万事总是开头难，一旦火星生态循环初步形成，大自然的力量会帮助你进一步完成宜居化的改造。<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1395760/extras/c552ce976857d76a43e19bb6c318196a.avif?t=1760234871\" width=623 height=177 /></span><br><br>你已经完成过重塑火星的壮举了，但也许在另一个平行世界，人类有着另外的动机去改造这颗星球。<br><br>也许是建立起一个没有活人的机械帝国，也许是全是底层人民前往艰苦开垦，也许去火星的全都是富家公子哥，也许地球早已断绝了和火星的一切通讯往来……<br><br>在新建游戏时，你可以选择这些不同的故事背景，带着不同的游戏设定，去体验不一样的改造火星之旅。<br><br>没准再过几十年，你选的这个大背景就照进了现实。那时的你也许正在前往火星的客运船上，看着背后的地球一点点缩小，至少你能拍拍胸脯告诉身边朋友：放轻松，这流程我熟。<br><br><br>希望这款游戏能给你开启一场特别的火星生存和殖民之旅。如果你对殖民火星有着浓厚的兴趣，可以进一步了解现实世界中各路大神们真正的火星重塑计划，也许他们正需要像我你这样平凡或不平凡人的关注。",
